public class PhotoEntry
extends SCModel<SCView>

POD (Plain Old Data) model that represents a photo that has been taken in the application. It has methods accessor methods for all its properties, which include a unique identifier, time stamp of when the photo was taken, a tag that is associated with a particular skin condition, and a file path that points to the actual image file. The setter methods notify any view that listens for changes in the PhotoEntry. Serves as the main model in the MVC paradigm.
